---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Irene Wang — Ongoing Practice"
  description="Design, AI, smart environments, and ongoing curiosities. "
>
  <div class="home">
    <section class="home-hero">
      <div class="home-hero-copy">
        <p class="home-kicker">PERSONAL WEBSITE / WORK / EXPERIMENTS / RESEARCH</p>

        <h1 class="home-title">
          <span>Irene Wang</span>
        </h1>
        <h1 class="home-title">
          <span>— Ongoing Practice</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="home-lead">
         <span class="home-lead-en">
            Design, AI, smart environments, and ongoing curiosities.
          </span>
        
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="home-entry-grid card-grid" aria-label="Main content paths">
      <a class="entry-card" href="/design">
        <div class="entry-card-top">
          <p class="entry-card-meta">Design work</p>
          <span class="entry-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h2>设计作品</h2>
          <p>Spatial, visual, interface, and concept-driven design work.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>

      <a class="entry-card" href="/projects">
        <div class="entry-card-top">
          <p class="entry-card-meta">Practice projects</p>
          <span class="entry-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h2>实践项目</h2>
          <p>Experiments, prototypes, making processes, and built outcomes.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>

      <a class="entry-card" href="/ai">
        <div class="entry-card-top">
          <p class="entry-card-meta">AI practice</p>
          <span class="entry-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h2>AI 尝试</h2>
          <p>Tools, workflows, prompting, prototypes, and applied AI thinking.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>

      <a class="entry-card" href="/research">
        <div class="entry-card-top">
          <p class="entry-card-meta">Academic research</p>
          <span class="entry-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="entry-card-body">
          <h2>学术研究</h2>
          <p>Questions, papers, references, and evolving research interests.</p>
        </div>
        <span class="entry-card-cta">进入页面</span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="home-about" aria-labelledby="home-about-title">
      <div class="home-about-grid">
        <div class="home-about-copy">
          <h2 id="home-about-title">About me</h2>
          <p>
            我关心设计、技术、AI 与智能环境交汇的地方，也持续观察空间、系统与人的关系如何被重新组织。
          </p>
          <p>
          I am fascinated by the intersection of design, technology, AI and intelligent environments, and I keep observing how the relationships among space, systems and people are being restructured.
          </p>
          <p>
            作品、实验、研究与书写，对我来说是同一件事的不同切面。
          </p>
          <p>
            Works, experiments, research and writing are different facets of one and the same thing to me.
          </p>
          <p>
            这里既展示结果，也保留过程——一些仍在生长中的方法、判断与感受。
          </p>
          <p>
            It presents both outcomes and preserves the process — methodologies, judgments, and sensibilities still in the making.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="home-about-side">
          <div class="home-about-card">
            <p class="home-about-label">Focus：Design / AI / Smart Environments / Research</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="home-about-actions">
            <a class="home-inline-link" href="/resume">查看简历</a>
          </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
